heading: Who are we?
description: Dublin High School Aerospace is a club dedicated to pushing the boundaries of plane and rocket discovery and innovation. Our mission is to inspire and educate the next generation of aerospace engineers and scientists, fostering a passion for discovery and technological advancement.
